    <item>
      <title>德意志银行认为，如果债券溃败继续</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/deutsche-bank-sees-fed-doing-emergency-qe-if-bond-rout-goes-on</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据德意志银行AG的数据，如果短暂推动美国长期借贷成本超过5％的溃败，美联储将需要介入稳定国库市场。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-09/deutsche-bank-sees-fed-doing-emergency-qe-if-bond-rout-goes-on</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 10:38:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普说，对制药的“主要关税”即将推出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-09/trump-says-major-tariff-on-pharma-coming-soon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统周二表示，他对制药药物的长期征收关税将很快推出，而无需提供计划中的征税的细节。彭博情报公司的Sam Fazeli还有更多。 （来源：彭博）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-04-09/trump-says-major-tariff-on-pharma-coming-soon</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 09 Apr 2025 10:36:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
